    "remarks_html": "<p>Response to a clan disband request.</p>\n<p><strong>Status</strong> is one of the <a href=\"/document/4/clan-system-overview\">Clan Message Codes</a>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>0x00</code>: Successfully disbanded</li>\n<li><code>0x02</code>: Too soon because the clan is not old enough (must be one week old)</li>\n<li><code>0x07</code>: Not authorized because you are not the clan leader</li>\n<li><code>0x08</code>: Not allowed</li>\n</ul>",
